		"description": "<p>At 15th level, when you use your @UUID[Compendium.a5e-bloody-heretics.bloody-heretics.Item.Rw64mkIKwTispsrX]{Sanguine Reach} feature, you may expend an extra hit die to infuse the blood and increase its potency. The reach granted by your Sanguine Reach increases to 20 feet, and the amount of damage you inflict with your Sanguine Transference is doubled for your turn. If you do not currently have a use of your Sanguine Transference when you activate this ability, you gain one additional use of it as part of this ability. Once you have used this ability, you may not do so again until you complete a long rest.</p>",
